snippet.title: Vivid World | Official Trailer 2023
snippet.description: Vivid World is a completely new party-building, roguelike, autobattler　strategy game! The story takes place in the Netherworld, a land ruled by demons. Utilize and master our protagonist, Lemuria's new Jewel Magic to conquer strange dungeons.
